7. FILES
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  validate_inputs.py             -- Parses and validates all inputs; runs
                                    quick factoring (trial division, Pollard's
                                    rho, Pollard's p-1); writes N.txt for
                                    CADO-NFS.

  solve_stage10.py               -- Main solver: RSA decryption (Miller-Rabin
                                    primality check, modular inverse, M=C^d mod N)
                                    and DES/Triple-DES decryption with automatic
                                    English plaintext detection.

  shorter_message_stage10.txt    -- RSA ciphertext C (155-digit decimal integer).

  longer_message_stage10.uue     -- UUencoded DES ciphertext (longer message).

  text.d                         -- Raw binary DES ciphertext, decoded from
                                    the .uue file (200 bytes, 25 DES blocks).

  N.txt                          -- Plain decimal modulus N, written by
                                    validate_inputs.py for CADO-NFS input.

  factoring_log.txt              -- Full CADO-NFS output log (~18.5 hour run).

  plaintext.txt                  -- Decrypted English plaintext (written by
                                    solve_stage10.py on successful decryption).

  README                         -- This file.
